Sentencas: Micro-tubular, solid oxide fuel cells consisting of nickel, yttria-stabilized zirconia (Ni-YSZ) anode, yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte and lanthanum strontium cobaltite ferrite-gadolinium doped ceria (LSCF-GDC) cathode have been developed and operated under single-chamber conditions, utilizing methane/air mixture.
Titulo: Silver modified cathode for a micro-tubular, single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The cell performance was compared with a silver modified cathode by the addition of 10wt% silver-paste in LSCF-GDC cathode.
Titulo: Silver modified cathode for a micro-tubular, single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The cells with and without silver addition yielded maximum power densities of 118.75 mW cm(-2) and 61.53 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Silver modified cathode for a micro-tubular, single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The results demonstrate that silver is a good candidate for enhancing the oxidation reduction kinetics via improved adsorption, desorption, dissociation and subsequent diffusion.
Titulo: Silver modified cathode for a micro-tubular, single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: However, long term performance of the silver modified cathode is not guaranteed under single-chamber conditions.
Titulo: Silver modified cathode for a micro-tubular, single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell
